{"type": "article", "id": 24021, "title": "店铺设计得这么潮，只是为了卖刀", "description": "这家迷你的日本小企业卖刀、卖包装盒，也卖菜板。", "date": "2016-03-17T14:43:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 8578, "name": "刀具"}, {"id": 25041, "name": "展示厅"}, {"id": 50, "name": "日本"}, {"id": 25042, "name": "Tadafusa"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 17, "praise_count": 250, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702113029UyNOdTR4x9EMQtP8.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>日本新潟市的 Sanjo 镇有着 400 多年的铸铁历史。早在 17 世纪初的江户时代，政府官员们就带着熟练的铁匠来到此地，教农民们锻造铁具以补贴收入。400 年后，这里也被人们称为“铁匠之乡”。这里诞生了不少本土刀具品牌，<a href=\"http://www.tadafusa.com\">Tadafusa 就是其中一个，中文名为“庖丁工房”</a>。</p>\n<p>最近，庖丁工房在工厂旁<a href=\"http://www.spoon-tamago.com/2016/03/16/tadafusa-a-new-hand-forged-japanese-knife-showroom-by-yusuke-seki/\">布置了一间全透明的陈列室</a>，展示架设计得很科学，值得刀具厂商们借鉴。</p>\n<p>庖丁工房一向将云杉作为切菜板，以此为灵感，建筑师 Ysuke Seki 在设计透明展示厅时，也使用了大量的云杉。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113023c46UoLk1xT5iAMEB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">这就是刀具品牌 Tadafusa 的展示厅了</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113023t2rf7jl4XvIagPZG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">展示厅位于一个全透明的玻璃盒子内，有两扇侧滑的玻璃门</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113024Ih1YzaspXdrJG7Z4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">刀具被整齐地摆放在定做的刀架上</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021130257yfoTRZi5LEeanHm.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">这就是刀架的细节图了，它可以变换位置</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113025M4uBblfswW5zPCJ3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113026d0unxljFISVyDkEH.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">展示空间内部大多为原始木材</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113026vTqCWV9JNuFrfbXn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021130270mFynQVDJMvzA2dj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113027Zmxui9MsYhcIVyUj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>“庖丁工房”成立于 1948 年，那一年创始人  Sone Torasaburo 只有 23 岁，一开始他制造各种刀具，包括镰刀和短剑等等，后来他逐渐专注在厨房用刀领域。直到今天，“庖丁工房”也只是个迷你企业，但他们的产品赢得了不少设计奖项。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113028Nd2yt4k6Q7BSbL9M.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66233766\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">厨房用刀</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113028F12AWXqVavCmK7eO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66233766\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">这是刀具的包装盒</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113028Qwmkadef83sgnjvX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66233766\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">也售卖菜板欸</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p>题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.spoon-tamago.com/2016/03/16/tadafusa-a-new-hand-forged-japanese-knife-showroom-by-yusuke-seki/\">spoon-tamago</a></p>\n\n"}